==古生物學==
[[File:Keratinous_sheaths_of_Borealopelta_and_analogues.png|thumb]] 
北方盾龍具有偽裝保護色的發現證實了儘管其體型大仍處於掠食者的威脅之中，背部裝甲主要用途為防禦而非展示。<ref name=desc/>棘刺則具有防禦和潛在展示（物種識別、吸引配偶）的雙重用途。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Brown|first1=C. M.|title=An exceptionally preserved armored dinosaur reveals the morphology and allometry of osteoderms and their horny epidermal coverings|journal=PeerJ|date=2017|volume=5|pages=e4066|doi=10.7717/peerj.4066|pmid=29201564|pmc=5712211}}</ref>

對標本胃內容物的檢驗發現蕨類是其主要食物，佔了最後一餐的大部分，並表明牠是高度專一性的攝食者。木炭也佔了內容物的約6%，得出這隻北方盾龍在一次野火過後至該地區覓食。Brown和同僚推測，這些蕨類在被攝取時已處於生長季節中，這表明這隻北方盾龍在初夏或仲夏時攝食，並於數小時後死亡。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Brown|first1=C. M.|last2=Greenwood|first2=D. E.|last3=Kalyniuk|first3=J. E.|last4=Braman|first4=D. R.|last5=Henderson|first5=D. M.|last6=Greenwood|first6=C. L.|last7=Basinger|first7=J. F.|date=2020|title=Dietary palaeoecology of an Early Cretaceous armoured dinosaur (Ornithischia; Nodosauridae) based on floral analysis of stomach contents|journal=Royal Society|volume=7|issue=6|pages=200305|doi=10.1098/rsos.200305|issn=20545703}}</ref>

==古生態學==
[[File:Borealopelta_Royal_Tyrrell_2.jpg|thumb]]
森科爾的北方盾龍保存於{{link-en|淨水組|Clearwater Formation}}{{link-en|威比斯考層|Clearwater Formation}}的海相[[砂岩|砂岩]]及[[頁岩|頁岩]]，年代估計為距今約1.12億至1.1億年前的白堊紀早期阿爾比階。<ref name=desc/>當時此地區由[[西部內陸海道|西部內陸海道]]圍繞<ref name=nat_geo1 /><ref name=Mossop19>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ags.gov.ab.ca/publications/wcsb_atlas/a_ch19/ch_19.html |title=The Geological Atlas of the Western Canada Sedimentary Basin, Chapter 19: Cretaceous Mannville Group of the Western Canada Sedimentary Basin |others=Compiled by Mossop, G.D. and Shetsen, I. |author=Canadian Society of Petroleum Geologists and Alberta Geological Survey |year=1994 |accessdate=2013-08-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814133127/http://www.ags.gov.ab.ca/publications/wcsb_atlas/a_ch19/ch_19.html |archivedate=2013-08-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而威比斯考沉積物沉積於離海海域環境。<ref name=desc/>

這隻北方盾龍可能在洪水事件被沖到海洋，浮腫的屍體可能漂浮數週直到它破裂而沉沒，<ref name=nat_geo1 />以背部朝下姿勢沉降至海床、並有足夠的重力得以迅速埋進海底沉積物。估計體液流出前已有大約15公分的沉積物埋在屍體上，可由沉積物中保存的流體溢散痕跡、且體腔充滿沙子得到證明。屍體沉到海床後不久周邊即產生了[[菱鐵礦|菱鐵礦]][[結核_(地質學)|結核]]，得以防止屍體被侵蝕、將皮膚和皮內成骨保存下來。<ref name=desc/>

